    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Loose covers for furniture, often tailored and close fitting, but easily slipped on and off. Used to protect the finer upholstery materials beneath from soil or wear, to conceal shabby upholstery, or to enhance the decorative scheme of an interior.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
